'''Park Soo-young''' (waxay dhalatay Sebteembar 3, 1996), oo loo yaqaan magaca masraxa '''Joy''', waa heesaa Koonfur Kuuriya iyo atariisho. Waxay ka soo muuqatay xubin ka mid ah kooxda gabdhaha Kuuriyada Koofureed Red Velvet bishii Ogosto 2014. Marka laga reebo waxqabadyada kooxda, waxay ku yeelatay doorar ee taxanaha telefishanka ''The Liar and His Lover'' (2017) iyo ''[[Tempted]]'' (2018).

